        {
            "title": "融創中國據報磋商新一輪債務重組 建議將所有離岸債轉為股本",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外電引知知情人士報道指，融創中國(01918)正磋商進行新一輪債務重組，包括建議將所有離岸債轉為股本。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道指，融創已就此與部分主要債權人磋商；債權人可以選擇的選項，包括不同轉換期的強制性可轉換債券，最終將轉換為股票，而可轉債定價等細節仍在討論中，最終方案或有調整，但相信重組條款很快便會公布。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14855877-%e8%9e%8d%e5%89%b5%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e7%a3%8b%e5%95%86%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%80%e8%bc%aa%e5%82%b5%e5%8b%99%e9%87%8d%e7%b5%84-%e5%bb%ba%e8%ad%b0%e5%b0%87%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e9%9b%a2%e5%b2%b8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01918.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 12:25:40",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱窄幅爭持 恒指半日升40點報21457點 芯片與藥股受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股連彈5日後，今早重歸平淡，於10天線附近反覆爭持；美國擬對芯片與藥品加徵關稅，相關股份早市壓力相對明顯。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Semiconductor_Industry-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Semiconductor_Industry-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早原本跟隨外圍繼續高開，於競價時段開升186點、報21603點，但即成半日高位，於上午10時過後展開窄幅爭持局面，最低曾見21349點，跌68點，早市大部份時間在10天線(最新約為21388點)附近上落；恒指中中午收報21457點，升40點或0.19%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Semiconductor_Industry-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Semiconductor_Industry-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"上海復旦官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/01385-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"上海復旦官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/01385-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">上海復旦官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-web_09866.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-web_09866.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：蔚來官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Semiconductor_Industry-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"上海復旦官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/01385-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">上海復旦官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-web_09866.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：蔚來官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跑輸大市，半日跌45點或0.91%，報4969點；國企指數升8點或0.11%，報7974點。主板半日成交1087.96億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升43點，報21459點，高水1點。科指期貨跌46點，報4973點，高水3點。國指期貨跌9點，報7972點，低水3點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國商務部發布通知，表示將調查進口芯片和半導體製造設備，以及藥品和藥物成分包括成品藥對美國國家安全的影響，令人顧慮美國將對芯片與藥品加徵關稅。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片與半導體相關股受壓，中芯國際(00981)跌3.16%，報46元；華虹半導體(01347)也跌1.67%，報35.35元；上海復旦(01385)更挫5.35%，報25.65元；英諾賽科(02577)則跌2.62%，報39.05元；ASMPT(00522)跌0.98%，報50.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥股亦見回吐，翰森製藥(03692)跌2.63%，報22.2元；藥明康德(02359)跌1.51%，報52.15元；石藥(01093)跌1.39%，報5.69元；藥明生物(02269)跌0.47%，報21.1元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"上海復旦官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/01385-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"上海復旦官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/01385-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">上海復旦官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">有傳美國總統特朗普考慮推出一系列關稅相關紓緩措施，包括暫時豁免進口汽車關稅，好讓美國汽車企業有時間調整供應鏈。不過，在港上市車股今早依然普遍向下。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地車股龍頭比亞迪(01211)跌0.59%，報373.8元；吉利汽車(00175)也跌0.12%，報16.52元；理想汽車(02015)跌2.64%，報90.35元；小鵬汽車(09868)挫3.51%，報78.25元，成為表現最差科指成分股。蔚來(09866)則成為「蔚小理」當中唯一報升的股份，升0.36%，報27.95元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-web_09866.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-web_09866.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：蔚來官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他重磅科股則互有升跌，昨天已逆市報跌的小米(01810)，今早再跌1.04%，報42.75元。「ATMXJ」其餘4隻股份則反覆偏好，騰訊(00700)微升0.13%，報454.6元；京東(09618)也升0.14%，報146.8元；美團(03690)今日正式推即時零售品牌「美團閃購」，股價升0.27%，報146.3元；阿里巴巴(09988)更是撐市主力，漲1.29%，報109.6元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，映恩生物(09606)今日登場，早市表現應超出不少人的預期。該股甫開市即見181元，較招股價94.6元高91.33%，最高曾衝上222元，高於招股價1.35倍；中午收報214.8元，仍比招股價高1.27倍，半日成交已達17.9億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14855863-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e7%aa%84%e5%b9%85%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%8740%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b121457%e9%bb%9e-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%88%87%e8%97%a5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-4.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 12:16:03",
